Additional OmniAnalytics Customizations

A Vlocity Web Tracking Event Type can have an Inclusion Rule, which specifies a true-or-false condition that determines whether an event is sent to a third-party analytics vendor such as Google Analytics.

Vlocity OmniAnalytics can support other third-party analytics vendors aside from Google Analytics.

The code that a Vlocity Web Tracking Configuration uses to communicate with a third-party analytics vendor can reside in either a Visualforce page or a static resource. If you use the Safari browser, your Vlocity Web Tracking Configuration must reference a static resource.
